    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Pure linen that is a suitable choice for painters' canvas; Belgian linens are generally considered the finest of linen grades. Some types are especially woven or selected for artists' purposes.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
